{"type": "article", "id": 12504, "title": "智能手机壳把手机变DV", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-23T07:53:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125742krN0MqZ6JGFe415t.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自美国的 Lumenati 工作室推出了一款智能手机壳，可以把 iPhone 6 或是 6S 嵌在里面，变成一个便携的 DV 使用，它带有一个手柄方便握住使用，你还可以选择广角镜头，鱼眼镜头，长焦镜头等多种镜头。同时，和手机壳配套的还有一个 Lumenati Cinematic App，可以用来对拍摄的视频进行简单的后期编辑。这是他们的<a href=\"http://cinematicsmartcase.com/\" target=\"_blank\">官方网站</a>，点击可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140231WrgLqh2QDTxP9nIv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140232gGiPOyH1ktRLeZ3f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72982885\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261402324czqYV2MlFwGhZNd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140233rVbojSkm0PyIpi3t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261402336Io8SmzJGZjNCBUE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140233m3HFNwDosptcYviB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61613692\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140234embXclJ6hNTjV705.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}